        "Per-frame dispatch is split into four entry points, called by Application.update in normative order: SceneManager.fixedUpdate (zero or more times), SceneManager.update, SceneManager.draw, then SceneManager._drawTransition last, so the fade overlay always sits above both scene and app draw systems."
