          "description": "Switch to scene (or clear to null), ending the previously active scene permanently. No-op when scene is already active. An optional fade transition runs the swap at full opacity. The new scene completes load()+init() before the old one is torn down, so there is no blank frame between them, and the outgoing scene keeps running until the switch boundary is crossed."
